#: src/MainGrid.vala:65
msgid "Decide how often Badger should remind you to relax these:"
msgstr ""
"Entscheide, wie oft Badger dich daran erinnern soll, diese zu entspannen:"

#: src/MainGrid.vala:136 src/MainGrid.vala:146
#, c-format
msgid "%.0f min"
msgstr "%.0f min"

